<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ OVERVIEW ═══ -->
<section class="section" id="overview">
  <div class="section-label">01 — Introduction</div>
  <h2 class="section-title"><span class="icon">⚡</span>What is Gondola?</h2>

  <div class="info-box">
    <strong>Gondola</strong> is a high-precision, autonomous AI coding platform designed for senior-level software engineering tasks. It is specifically architected and optimized for the Zhipu AI GLM Series (GLM-4.7, GLM-5, GLM-5.1) while also supporting Claude, GPT, and Kimi models — focusing on surgical discovery, rigorous safety, and context efficiency.
  </div>

  <div class="card-grid">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-accent-line" style="background: var(--cyan);"></div>
      <div class="card-title">🧠 Cognitive Persistence</div>
      <div class="card-desc">Agent state (thought checkpoints, file hashes, action history) is written to a hidden Git branch — <code>_gondola_shadow</code> — without touching the working directory.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-accent-line" style="background: var(--green);"></div>
      <div class="card-title">🔬 Surgical Discovery</div>
      <div class="card-desc">Moves away from "blind reading" via <code>map_project()</code>, <code>symbol_jump()</code>, <code>smart_context()</code>, and Tree-sitter AST skeletons — targeted, zero-waste exploration.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-accent-line" style="background: var(--red);"></div>
      <div class="card-title">🛡️ Rigorous Safety</div>
      <div class="card-desc">Every edit goes through <strong>RiskAnalyzer</strong> scoring (0–100+). Hash-verification blocks edits if a file changed on disk since the agent last read it.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-accent-line" style="background: var(--magenta);"></div>
      <div class="card-title">🎛️ Daft UI</div>
      <div class="card-desc">A high-performance, immersive web UI cockpit: Living Avatar, Context Pulse, Perimeter Chase animations, Git Hub, and Quick Macros.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-accent-line" style="background: var(--yellow);"></div>
      <div class="card-title">📦 ~60 Tools</div>
      <div class="card-desc">File ops, code analysis, git, testing, web search, image ops, knowledge base, transactions — all registered in a typed schema with pre-flight validation.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-accent-line" style="background: var(--blue);"></div>
      <div class="card-title">🔁 Loop Prevention</div>
      <div class="card-desc">Exploration budget, duplicate-call detection, exact-loop pattern matching, and reasoning enforcement prevent infinite tool loops on weaker models.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

