      <div class="card-desc">Ctags-format symbol index for O(1) <code>symbol_jump()</code> lookup. Built in background during session start. Queried with <code>grep ^symbolname\t</code> for speed.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-accent-line" style="background: var(--blue);"></div>
      <div class="card-title">Auto-Learning on done()</div>
      <div class="card-desc">When the agent calls <code>done(summary)</code>, <code>AgentState.generate_learning()</code> creates a structured knowledge entry (task, files modified, hints) and saves it via <code>save_knowledge()</code> for future sessions.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
