              <tr><td style="color:var(--text-dim);">1–4</td><td>Note it, no position</td></tr>
              <tr><td style="color:var(--yellow);">5–6</td><td>Forming — identify gaps</td></tr>
              <tr><td style="color:var(--cyan);">7–8</td><td>Standard sizing</td></tr>
              <tr><td style="color:var(--green);">9–10</td><td>Size to maximum</td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="panel panel-blue">
