      </div>

      <div class="tool-group">
        <div class="tool-group-header">Scanning &amp; Research</div>
        <div class="tool-list">
          <div class="tool-item"><span class="tool-name">get_market_movers()</span><span class="tool-desc">Top gainers, losers, or most actives — filter by price and volume</span></div>
