<section id="memory">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="section-tag">Memory System</span>
    <h2 class="section-title">MemoryV2 — Tiered persistent memory.</h2>
    <p class="section-lead">Persists across sessions and strategy switches. Every thesis, observation, trade outcome, and lesson is stored and recalled on the next cycle.</p>

    <div class="memory-tier">
      <div class="tier-indicator">
